      "text": [
        " مَنْ قَذَفَ امْرَأَتَهُ قَبْلَ أَنْ يَدْخُلَ بِهَا جُلِدَ الْحَدَّ وَ هِيَ امْرَأَتُهُ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from Muhammad Bin Isa Bin Ubeyd, from Yunus, from Muhammad Bin Muzarab, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The one who accuses his wife before he copulates with her would be whipped one Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>), and she would (still) be his wife’."
        ]
